pageContext.claim: “The folks behind me know all about MS-13 and how violent and vicious they are, and where they come from. And they all come from the same place. And they all come in the same way; they come right across that border.”
pageContext.analysis: It's misleading to suggest that all MS-13 members come "right across the border." While gang holds extensive territory in Central America and has roots in El Salvador, it originated in Los Angeles to protect Salvadoran immigrants.
